Instalando Aplicaciones en linux mint :D
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Git :

	- sudo apt-get install git
	- sudo apt-get install git-core

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Django:
	- sudo apt-get install python-setuptools
	- sudo easy_install pip
	- pip install virtualenv
		virtualenv acpop
		source acpop/bin/activate
		pip install django 
	
	ojo: - pip install -r requirements.txt
	- pip install djangorestframework

	- pip install gunicorn

Intalando librerias en Django:

en linux mint :
- pip install PIL
- pip install PIL --allow-external PIL --allow-unverified PIL

si no funciona, correr el siguiente codigo:

sudo apt-get install build-essential autoconf libtool pkg-config python-opengl python-imaging python-pyrex python-pyside.qtopengl idle-python2.7 qt4-dev-tools qt4-designer libqtgui4 libqtcore4 libqt4-xml libqt4-test libqt4-script libqt4-network libqt4-dbus python-qt4 python-qt4-gl libgle3 python-dev

* recordar que para instalarlo en un virtualenv no poner sudo


--------------------------------------------------------------------


en heroku si nos da error por la clave publica:

heroku keys:add ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub


--------------------------------------------------------------------
instalar jdk & NetBeans

chmod +x jdk-7u60-nb-8-linux-x64.sh
sh ./jdk-7u60-nb-8-linux-x64.sh

--------------------------------------------------------------------

sudo apt-get install mysql-server

mysql -u root -p


--------------------------------------------------------------------

Install Spotify in Ubuntu 14.04 & Linux Mint

sudo sh -c 'echo "deb http://repository.spotify.com stable non-free" >> /etc/

sudo apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv-keys 94558F59

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install spotify-client

















